Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.89,0:00:02.58,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.58,0:00:03.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,咦 怎麼沒人來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.96,0:00:05.69,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.69,0:00:07.04,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.04,0:00:09.38,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,不用叫這麼多次我也會來的 就不能等等嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.53,0:00:13.59,Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\an2}{\1c&HA86C6F&}Re{\1c&HA9AB4B&}:{\1c&H7D60CC&}小{\1c&H4396E0&}劇場 {\1c&H000000&}之四
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.60,0:00:18.17,SignC,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H9A7CFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}小{\1c&H4FB4FF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}劇場{\3c&HFFFFFF&\1c&HB8B80F&}❹{\1c&HBB878E&\3c&HFFFFFF&}主{\1c&H4FB4FF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}人{\1c&HC2BA20&\3c&HFFFFFF&}和、他{\1c&H4FB4FF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}的{\1c&H9A7CFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}女{\1c&HC2BA20&\3c&HFFFFFF&}僕們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.12,0:00:16.38,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 服務生是蘿莉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.38,0:00:17.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,是違反勞動法的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:19.69,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,氣死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.69,0:00:20.42,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}就算如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.05,0:00:23.44,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,碧翠絲在這裡的話也就是說 這裡是哥德蘿莉咖啡廳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.44,0:00:24.54,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,不 蘿莉咖啡廳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.54,0:00:25.87,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,想打架嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.87,0:00:27.53,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 吵架了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.53,0:00:29.56,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,店長來了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.56,0:00:32.70,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,哇 看起來有種不好的預感的店長來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.70,0:00:34.59,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,你這說法真失禮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:38.76,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,我這咖啡廳店是不會做讓老大爺覺得難堪的買賣的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:41.07,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼說倒是更讓人覺得可疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.07,0:00:43.55,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,客人 既然來了咖啡廳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.55,0:00:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不點點什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.97,0:00:48.24,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,也是 肚子也餓了 那就先點點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:48.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.96,0:00:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本店人氣第一 喵喵蛋包飯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.51,0:00:53.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,很吸引人 但是感覺好危險
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.27,0:00:54.83,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 這店果然太危險了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.83,0:00:56.78,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,當然沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:00:59.96,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,這樣說像這樣健全的店鋪 真是太失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.96,0:01:02.05,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,對對 你也太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.05,0:01:03.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為你這樣說了才可疑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.90,0:01:05.48,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,覺得不爽那就請回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.48,0:01:08.12,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,好好好 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.12,0:01:10.86,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,那就這個 人氣第一的喵喵蛋包飯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.86,0:01:13.30,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,好 喵喵蛋包飯一個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:14.99,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.99,0:01:16.93,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,這氣氛不太像咖啡廳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.44,0:01:20.98,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 不過氣氛是奇怪了點 也有可能是普通的店嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.02,0:01:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.06,0:01:27.21,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.21,0:01:30.32,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,客人快給他加油 看他這麼努力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.32,0:01:32.73,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,喵喵蛋包飯原來是這個意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.73,0:01:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗚喵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.89,0:01:38.11,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,今天的帕克醬也很拚命在運蛋包飯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:40.02,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,難道這裡是喵喵咖啡廳？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.02,0:01:41.56,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,也許就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.56,0:01:44.54,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,但這蛋包飯對於貓來說不是太大了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:46.20,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,這是喵喵蛋包飯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.20,0:01:49.49,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如說是點了這麼大的喵喵蛋包飯的你的錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.49,0:01:50.48,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,我的錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:53.61,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝啦帕克
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.61,0:01:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.78,0:01:58.82,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,喔 難道說在這世界 帕克只是一隻普通的貓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.82,0:01:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.65,0:02:02.11,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,帕克 竟然不能說話...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.11,0:02:03.52,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,不 我能說話的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.52,0:02:04.35,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.86,0:02:05.74,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,嘛算了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.74,0:02:08.41,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,帕克搖搖晃晃給我送來的喵喵蛋包飯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.41,0:02:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起來還挺好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.20,0:02:11.92,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是人氣第一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.92,0:02:12.83,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.83,0:02:15.19,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,我就開動啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.19,0:02:17.22,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼你開始吃起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.22,0:02:20.28,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,因為是喵喵蛋包飯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:21.65,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,客人你才是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.65,0:02:23.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,要吃還是要說話你倒是選一個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.19,0:02:25.52,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,居然選吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.97,0:02:28.52,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是選吃啊
